  "product": {
    "id": 8404755743036,
    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board SK-E09 (820mm x 460mm)",
    "body_html": "<p> </p>\n<div data-content-field=\"excerpt\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\">\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\"> <span>The SK-E09 stands out as a premium option in the SeaKing range, characterised by its </span><span>ergonomic design. It includes a spacious knife tray positioned at the front for quick and easy access, </span><span>along with a deep storage sink featuring a drain. A distinctive feature of this board is its raised lip </span><span>around the sides and back, ensuring secure retention of items even in rough conditions. </span>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Handcrafted </span><span>using top-grade composite materials, it incorporates a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board for </span><span>durability. Crafted to meet the demands of serious anglers, this board combines functionality with </span><span>premium quality materials, making it an excellent choice for fishing enthusiasts seeking reliability and </span><span>performance on the water.</span></p>\n<b id=\"docs-internal-guid-eff1bc17-7fff-9f22-7b22-7543c63b32ac\"></b>\n</div>",
